# id: InfoReceiver -> String executeInfoRequest(URI infoUrl, HttpHeaders headers)_
commentText:
Perform an HTTP request to the SockJS "Info" URL._and return the resulting JSON response content, or raise an exception._

Note that as of 4.2 this method accepts a {@code headers} parameter._@param infoUrl the URL to obtain SockJS server information from_@param headers the headers to use for the request_@return the body of the response
